<div class="ru-story">
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title"> Allen &#038; Company Rises in Technology Sector <span class="divider">&nbsp;|&nbsp;</span></span><!-- end .title --> Marc Andreessen told The Wall Street Journal that Facebookâs hiring of Allen &#038; Company, a boutique investment bank, as an adviser on its initial public offering, was âan opportunity to repayâ the bank for previous work it had done for Facebook.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303636404579397112054095536"> WALL STREET JOURNAL </a></span></p>
